events.title: CID UC Weekly Meeting
events.description: Scheduled weekly meeting for the FBI's Criminal Investigative Division (CID), to be held in the CID Large Conference Room 3853. The invitation notes Skype information is available on the 'high side'.

keyFacts: The FBI's Criminal Investigative Division (CID) held a weekly meeting scheduled to start on February 22, 2018.
The meeting invitation was created on February 14, 2018, and was noted as a 'new invite' as of that date.
The invitation specifies that Skype information for the meeting is on the 'high side,' indicating the use of a secure or classified communication system.
